%h1 Getting Started
%h2 Install
%p
  Add this line in your Gemfile:
  %br
  %code gem "ui_bibz", '~> #{ UiBibzApp::Application::VERSION }'

%p
  Run this command:
  %br
  %code  bundle install

%h2 Assets Install
%p
  Put this line in:
  %code /app/assets/stylesheets/applications.css

  %pre
          ...
    \*= require ui_bibz
    \...

%p
  Put this line in:
  %code /app/assets/javascripts/applications.js
  %pre
          ...
    \//= require ui_bibz
    \...

  _Ps: You can use sass variables into Boostrap._

%h2 Simple form
%p
  Gem is compatible with
  = link_to "simple_form", "https://github.com/plataformatec/simple_form"
  \. All inputs fields can be used with
  %strong simple_form.

